('broadcast_looting_item_uncommon', 'That %item_link is exactly what I needed today.', 0, 0, '', 'Ce %item_link est exactement ce dont j’avais besoin aujourd’hui.', '%item_link ist genau das, was ich heute gebraucht habe.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_uncommon', 'I’ll never say no to a nice %item_link.', 0, 0, '', 'Je ne dis jamais non à une belle %item_link.', 'Zu einem schönen %item_link sag ich nie nein.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_uncommon', 'Another %item_link. I’ll take it, no complaints here.', 0, 0, '', 'Encore un %item_link. Je le prends, pas de soucis ici.', 'Noch ein %item_link. Ich nehm’s, keine Beschwerden.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_uncommon', 'At least %item_link has some use. Not the worst loot.', 0, 0, '', 'Au moins %item_link a une certaine utilité. Ce n’est pas le pire butin.', 'Zumindest hat %item_link eine Verwendung. Nicht der schlechteste Loot.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_uncommon', '%item_link might just be the one thing I need for the day.', 0, 0, '', 'Hmm, le lien %item_link pourrait bien être exactement ce dont j’ai besoin pour la journée.', 'Vielleicht ist %item_link genau das, was ich heute brauche.', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'nooo, I got %item_link', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'aww not this trash again %item_link', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'seem to be looting trash %item_link', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'well, it\'s better than nothing I guess %item_link', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'not sure what to do with %item_link', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Ugh, another %item_link. What did I do to deserve this?', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'This %item_link isn\'t even worth selling.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Great, just what I needed. More garbage: %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I\'ve seen better loot in a trash heap.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Looks like my luck ran out. %item_link is all I get.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'What am I supposed to do with %item_link? Seriously.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Not again! %item_link, you haunt me.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Guess I\'ll just add %item_link to the pile.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'If disappointment had a name, it would be %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Another day, another useless %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I bet no one else even wants %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Why do I always get stuck with %item_link?', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'This %item_link should come with a refund.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Oh look, more junk: %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', '%item_link is about as useful as a broken sword.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Guess I\'ll keep %item_link… for sentimental reasons?', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Well, at least %item_link doesn\'t smell bad.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'This is not what I signed up for! %item_link again?', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'My inventory is now 10% %item_link and 90% despair.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Maybe I can trade %item_link for something better… like a stick.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'This %item_link will make a fine doorstop.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'You\'d think they\'d at least polish %item_link before giving it out.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I guess %item_link is better than nothing. Barely.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', '%item_link? Really? I demand a recount!', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I wouldn\'t wish %item_link on my worst enemy.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Is %item_link cursed? Because it sure feels like it.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Well, this %item_link is going straight to the scrap dealer.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Why do I even bother? %item_link isn\'t worth the effort.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'The only thing worse than %item_link is two of them.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', '%item_link just screams "mediocrity."', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Oh… %item_link? Well, I guess it\'s better than absolutely nothing.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I had high hopes… but all I got was %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Hey, at least it\'s shiny! Oh, wait, it\'s just %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I\'m not crying, it\'s just… dust. And %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Yay! Oh… it\'s just %item_link. Never mind.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I didn\'t know disappointment had a physical form: %item_link.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Could\'ve been worse. Wait… no, it couldn\'t. %item_link is the worst.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Well, %item_link isn\'t going to sell itself… if it sells at all.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Huh, %item_link. I guess that\'s what luck looks like. Bad luck.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Oh no… not %item_link. Anything but that!', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I suppose %item_link will make a fine placeholder until something better comes along.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'What\'s this? %item_link? Hah, good one.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'This isn\'t loot; it\'s a practical joke. %item_link? Seriously?', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'If you squint really hard, %item_link almost looks valuable.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I bet someone out there might actually want %item_link. Not me, though.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Oh look, it\'s %item_link! … Wait, why am I excited?', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'This %item_link is so bad, even a vendor might refuse it.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I guess %item_link could double as a paperweight.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'Who left %item_link lying around? Oh, right. Fate did.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('broadcast_looting_item_poor', 'I\'ll keep %item_link… as a reminder to lower my expectations.', 0, 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
