('reply', 'well, that was a learning experience… never again.', 0, 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'gg, %s. I\'ll just be over here questioning my life choices.', 0, 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'you know what? I blame the healer.', 0, 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'well, %s, you\'ve officially ruined my evening.', 0, 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'at least I looked cool while losing.', 0, 2, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
