('reply', '%s, even murlocs laugh at you.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'remind me to go easy on you next time, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'you\'re my favorite target, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'at least you tried, %s. Sort of.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'you\'re my warm-up fight, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'By the Earthmother, %s, you were crushed.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, even the spirits are laughing at you.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'You\'ve made the ancestors proud, %s… of me.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, your defeat is as epic as a Frostmourne replica.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'I should\'ve been a bard, %s. I\'m writing songs about this kill.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'another victim for the history books, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'the Lich King would approve of that kill, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, your gear won\'t save you next time.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'even a Naaru couldn\'t heal you from that, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Elune\'s light didn\'t reach you in time, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'For the Horde! Another Alliance down, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, you fought like a kobold with no candle.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Lok\'tar, %s! Your defeat is my victory!', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'The Light couldn\'t save you this time, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Even the Naaru would laugh at your loss, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Another victory for the Horde! Sorry, %s... not really.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'By Elune, %s, I almost feel bad for you. Almost.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'You\'re weaker than a Stormwind recruit, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Feel the might of a true champion, %s!', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'That fight was easier than farming linen cloth, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Oops, %s, did I crit too hard?', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Should I have let you win, %s? Nah.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Do you need a rez, %s? I can wait.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, you went down faster than a gnome in a thunderstorm.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'That was almost fun, %s. Let\'s do it again!', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Hey %s, I hope you enjoy the view from the graveyard.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'This fight will go in my “easy wins” list, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Did you forget your cooldowns, %s? Rough.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Thanks for the warm-up, %s. Who\'s next?', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'You\'re tougher than a murloc, %s... barely.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'By the Sunwell, %s, you didn\'t stand a chance.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, your defeat will echo through the Shadowlands.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'The Earthmother smiles upon my victory, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'The ancestors guided my hand today, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Another fallen foe for the glory of the Horde, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, Elune\'s light must have abandoned you.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'You\'ll find no forgiveness in the Maelstrom, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'My blade thirsted for battle, %s, and it drank deeply.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Your spirit will haunt %zone_name, %s. A reminder of my triumph.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Rest well in the graveyard, %s. You\'ve earned it.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, bow before your new overlord!', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'That fight was over before it began, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, even Deathwing would laugh at your attempts.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Your loss will be sung by bards across Azeroth, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'I\'m unstoppable! You\'re just another name on my list, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'I could\'ve beaten you in greys, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Another soul for the Shadowlands, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Your defeat was inevitable, %s. I am Azeroth\'s champion.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, you\'ll need divine intervention next time.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, even the Scourge would be ashamed of that performance.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, should I slow down next time?', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Next time, try dodging, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, I\'ve seen critters put up more of a fight.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'That was cute, %s. Let\'s do it again.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, you\'d lose to a training dummy.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Careful, %s. I almost broke a sweat.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'You\'ll get me next time, %s. Maybe. Probably not.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Keep practicing, %s. You\'ll need it.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, was that your version of “trying”?', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, you\'re like a free loot chest.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'The Lich King sends his regards, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'By the Earthmother, %s, you were crushed.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, even Arthas would\'ve laughed at that.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Did the Bronze Dragonflight timewarp you into losing, %s?', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'You\'ll haunt %zone_name as a defeated spirit, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, your defeat will be the stuff of tavern jokes.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'This win goes straight to the Horde archives, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'Even the Naaru could not shine a light on your skills, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', 'The elements themselves aided my victory, %s.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
('reply', '%s, let\'s hope your respawn goes better than that fight.', 0, 3, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
